msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hateno Village is a village on the\n"
"edge of Hyrule.\n"
"\n"
"It was largely unaffected by the events\n"
"of the <2.se_co>Great Calamity<3.re_co>, so the people\n"
"there are pretty easygoing.\n"
"<4.so>I hear they even have a <5.se_co>research\n"
"center<6.re_co>...<7.pa> But folks tend to avoid the\n"
"weird scientist who lives there...\n"
"<8.so>Anyway, head north from here until you\n"
"reach a fork in the road. Then go east\n"
"and just follow the road.\n"
"It's a little far if you walk it, but with a\n"
"horse, you should get there in under\n"
"a day!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Leave it to Rensa to tell you about the\n"
"roads around this area.<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
