msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Everything looks just as it always has,\n"
"but the effects of the <2.se_co>Great Calamity<3.re_co>\n"
"still linger.\n"
"<4.so>For example, a lot of <5.se_co>monsters<6.re_co> come out\n"
"at night, so be careful when the\n"
"sun sets..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You're asking me now?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"There certainly are not as many as in\n"
"years past, but there are still quite a few\n"
"around...\n"
"<2.so>If you manage to catch one, let my\n"
"brother Tasseren know. He'll register the\n"
"horse for you!\n"
"My boys are wellsprings of information\n"
"about horses, but I'm sure you don't\n"
"need another lecture.\n"
"<3.so>After all, you're the one who beat me,\n"
"the guy who took second in the Hyrule\n"
"Horse-Taming Competition."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ya know, someone who can handle a\n"
"horse has a real leg up on the \n"
"competition when it comes to ladies...\n"
"I know what I'm talking about! I took\n"
"second in the Hyrule Horse-Taming\n"
"Competition!<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

